</div><div type="history" n="record">
<head>History of Recording</head>
<p>b. excavated in 1905; copied by Boulanger (notebook A.63, 23, whence B. 8-9, no 8, C 27); not reported subsequently. a. found by the NYU expedition in 1984 (<rs type="invNo">84.74</rs>)</p>
